# Offer of Internship: AI Intern

Date: [Date]

Dear [Candidate Full Name],

We are pleased to offer you a temporary internship position with Omninuera in the role of AI Intern. This letter outlines the principal terms of the internship. This is a draft offer and will be subject to review by Omninuera's Legal and HR teams.

## Position and Role
- **Role:** AI Intern  
- **Employment type:** Internship (temporary engagement). This internship is a training and project-based engagement and does not by itself create an employment relationship. The intern is not entitled to employee benefits (such as health insurance, paid leave, retirement benefits, etc.) unless expressly specified in writing by Omninuera.  
- **Duration:** 3 months.  
- **Start date:** [Start Date]  
- **Reporting manager:** [Reporting Manager]

## Work Location and Hours
- **Work location:** Fully remote. Candidate to be based in Bengaluru.  
- **Expected weekly commitment:** 20–40 hours per week. Work hours are flexible to accommodate remote work and study commitments; specific schedule will be agreed with your reporting manager.

## Stipend
- **Stipend:** INR 10,000 per month. This is expressly a stipend for the duration of the internship and should not be construed as a salary or wages subject to employment benefits.  
- **Stipend payment schedule:** Stipend will be paid monthly via bank transfer into the account details provided by you. Please provide bank details in the format requested: [Bank Details].

## Primary Responsibilities / Scope of Work
During the internship you will be expected to perform tasks including, but not limited to:
- Preparing and cleaning datasets for model training and evaluation.  
- Running model experiments, training runs, and hyperparameter tuning under supervision.  
- Assisting with model evaluation, performance analysis, and result interpretation.  
- Writing clear documentation of experiments, data provenance, and reproducible instructions.  
- Collaborating with the team on code reviews, design discussions, and knowledge sharing.

## Confidentiality and Intellectual Property
- **Confidentiality:** You will be required to maintain confidentiality of Omninuera’s proprietary information, trade secrets, and any non-public business, technical or financial information you access during the internship. This obligation continues after the internship ends.  
- **IP Assignment:** You agree that all inventions, discoveries, improvements, works of authorship, technical developments, code, data models, documents and other deliverables (collectively, “Work Product”) created, conceived, or reduced to practice by you, alone or with others, in the course of the internship, will be the exclusive property of Omninuera. You will assign and hereby assign all right, title and interest in such Work Product to Omninuera and will execute any documents necessary to effectuate such assignments.

## Termination and Early Exit
- Either party may terminate this internship with one (1) week’s written notice.  
- Omninuera may terminate the internship immediately for cause, including but not limited to material breach of this agreement, violation of company policies, gross misconduct, or breach of confidentiality obligations.

## Conditions of Offer
- This draft offer is subject to legal compliance review by Omninuera’s Legal team.  
- This offer is also conditional on any background verification checks Omninuera may require; continuation of the internship is contingent on satisfactory completion of such checks.

## Acceptance and Onboarding
To accept this offer, please sign and return a copy of this letter by [insert deadline if desired]. Upon acceptance, HR will provide onboarding instructions, access credentials, and any required documentation.

## Stipend Payment Details
- **Payment method:** Monthly bank transfer.  
- **Required bank details for stipend disbursement:** bank account holder name, account number, bank name, branch, IFSC code, and any other details required. (Placeholder: [Bank Details])

## Governing Law and Jurisdiction
- This offer and any dispute or claim arising out of or in connection with it shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of Bengaluru, India. The courts located in Bengaluru shall have exclusive jurisdiction.

## Miscellaneous
- Nothing in this letter constitutes an express or implied promise of continued engagement beyond the specified internship duration.  
- This letter, once accepted, constitutes the entire understanding between you and Omninuera relating to the internship and supersedes prior discussions (unless otherwise stated in a separate signed document).

